              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28720047/" class="">第142页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65707389/" class=" " title="小轩">小轩</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28720047">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">论客。宾朋杂沓，止堪交错觥筹；乍会泛交，仅须常品酬酢。惟素心同调，彼此畅适，清言雄辩，脱略形骸，始可呼童篝火，酌水点汤。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-25 22:36</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>论客。宾朋杂沓，止堪交错觥筹；乍会泛交，仅须常品酬酢。惟素心同调，彼此畅适，清言雄辩，脱略形骸，始可呼童篝火，酌水点汤。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







